videos.headline: Taylor makes the one-handed catch, but Cornhuskers force a fumble
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jonathan Taylor pulls in the skillful one-handed grab, but its gets stripped by Nebraska's JoJo Domann and recovered by Lamar Jackson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Taylor makes the one-handed catch, but Cornhuskers force a fumble) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska scores first on Mills' TD
videos.description: Cornhuskers' Dedrick Mills rushes the ball in up the middle for 12 yards and puts his team on the board first against Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Nebraska scores first on Mills' TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin takes kickoff 89 yards to the house
videos.description: Wisconsin answers with a touchdown of their own as Aron Cruickshank takes the kick all the way back for an 89-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Wisconsin takes kickoff 89 yards to the house) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: A.J. Taylor bounces off of tackles for another Badgers TD
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jack Coan launches the ball to A.J. Taylor, who hustles his way into the end zone for a 55-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (A.J. Taylor bounces off of tackles for another Badgers TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor scores the contested TD for Wisconsin
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor pushes past the Nebraska defense and gets the one-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Taylor scores the contested TD for Wisconsin) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Martinez connects with Spielman for a Nebraska TD
videos.description: Adrian Martinez locates JD Spielman in the end zone with a 23-yard pass and the Cornhuskers score late in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Martinez connects with Spielman for a Nebraska TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET
